Interface Command

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddBooking, AddCustomer, AddFlight, CancelBooking, DeleteCustomer, DeleteFlight, EditBooking, Help, ListBookings, ListBookingsCustomer, ListBookingsDate, ListBookingsFlight, ListCustomers, ListFlights, LoadGUI, NoOpCommand, ShowCustomer, ShowFlight
public interface Command
Represents an executable command that operates on the FlightBookingSystem.

Each command typically modifies or queries the system (e.g., adding flights, deleting customers). The HELP_MESSAGE provides a brief reference of all supported CLI commands.
